SELECT t1.FIPS, (t1.attribute - h1._avg) / h1._stddev as attribute FROM table as t1,

(SELECT AVG(h1.attribute) as _avg, STDDEV(h1.attribute) as _stddev FROM table) as h1

,

queryattributecrime rate correlation coefficient

CORR(attribute, crime_rate)

SELECT (AVG(t1.attribute *t2.crime_rate_per_100000) - AVG(t1.attribute)*AVG(t2.crime_rate_per_100000)) / (STDDEV(t1.attribute) * STDDEV(t2.crime_rate_per_100000)) as CORR FROM table t1, crime_rate t2

WHERE t1.FIPS = t2.FIPS
